text: Fernanda Loreto Urrejola Arroyo (born September 24, 1981) is a Chilean actress. She was born in Santiago de Chile. Her best known movie roles were in My Best Enemy (2005), Drama (2010) and Bring Me the Head of the Machine Gun Woman (2012). She will star in the 2021 Clint Eastwood movie Cry Macho. ==Other websites== * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Santiago Category:Chilean movie actors Category:Chilean television actors
